paragraph: Chelsea Cullen is an Australian pop singer. Cullen provided the singing voice of Helen Reddy in the 2019 biographical film, I Am Woman, for which she won an ARIA Music Award.

section: == Awards and nominations == | === ARIA Music Awards ===

paragraph: The ARIA Music Awards is an annual awards ceremony that recognises excellence, innovation, and achievement across all genres of Australian music. Cullen has received 1 nomination.
